  "apps": [
    {
      "id": "xinyao-signin",
      "name": "鑫耀光环签到",
      "keys": [
        "XYHG_Authorization",
        "XYHG_ExpireWarning"
      ],
      "settings": [
        {
          "id": "XYHG_Authorization",
          "name": "会员 Token",
          "val": "",
          "type": "textarea",
          "autoGrow": true,
          "rows": 3,
          "desc": "自动抓取的 Bearer Token，包含 vipcode。打开小程序后由 GetToken 脚本自动写入，也可手动粘贴。"
        },
        {
          "id": "XYHG_ExpireWarning",
          "name": "Token 过期预警（小时）",
          "val": 6,
          "type": "text",
          "desc": "Token 剩余时间低于此值时推送提醒，默认 6 小时。"
        }
      ],
      "author": "@辣堡",
      "repo": "https://github.com/a974881061",
      "icons": [
        "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/a974881061/Blue/refs/heads/main/icons/xygh.jpeg"
      ],
      "script": "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/a974881061/Blue/refs/heads/main/Scripts/xinyao_signin.js",
      "descs_html": [
        "<h4>一键安装（推荐）</h4>",
        "<p>Loon 插件页签 → 点击右上角 + → 粘贴以下链接：</p>",
        "<pre>https://raw.githubusercontent.com/a974881061/Blue/refs/heads/main/xinyao_signin.plugin</pre>",
        "<h4>激活 Token</h4>",
        "<ol>",
        "<li>安装插件后打开微信小程序「鑫耀光环」，触发 Token 自动抓取</li>",
        "<li>收到「会员 Token 已更新」通知后即可等待每日自动签到</li>",
        "</ol>"
      ]
    },
